summary:
- **General Meeting Results**: All resolutions (except withdrawn Resolutions 8 & 9) passed by poll with strong majority support (typically >90% in favor).  
- **Key Approved Items**:  
   - Ratification of prior share placements under ASX Listing Rules 7.1 and 7.1A.  
   - Approval for issuing broker options and employee performance rights/termination benefits to key personnel (Whittaker, Hancock, Rezos, Mcillree, Sondergaard).  

*No material trading or capital structure impacts identified beyond routine approvals.*
